colubrisWirelessClientMIB.description: Information for Colubris Networks client mode devices.

colubrisWirelessClientSSID.name: colubrisWirelessClientSSID
colubrisWirelessClientSSID.description: Service Set ID assigned to the device.

colubrisWirelessClientBSSID.name: colubrisWirelessClientBSSID
colubrisWirelessClientBSSID.description: When the client state is associated, this object identifies the MAC Address of the access point.

colubrisWirelessClientSignalLevel.name: colubrisWirelessClientSignalLevel
colubrisWirelessClientSignalLevel.description: Strength of the wireless signal (in dBm).

colubrisWirelessClientNoiseLevel.name: colubrisWirelessClientNoiseLevel
colubrisWirelessClientNoiseLevel.description: Level of local background noise (in dBm).

colubrisWirelessClientSNR.name: colubrisWirelessClientSNR
colubrisWirelessClientSNR.description: Relative strength of the signal level compared to the noise level.

colubrisWirelessClientConnectTime.name: colubrisWirelessClientConnectTime
colubrisWirelessClientConnectTime.description: Elapsed time in seconds since the device successfully associated with an access point.

colubrisWirelessClientAuthorizedState.name: colubrisWirelessClientAuthorizedState
colubrisWirelessClientAuthorizedState.description: Indicates if user traffic is allowed on the wireless port.

colubrisWirelessClientEncryptionStatus.name: colubrisWirelessClientEncryptionStatus
colubrisWirelessClientEncryptionStatus.description: Indicates the encryption method used to communicate with the access point.

colubrisWirelessClientTransmitRate.name: colubrisWirelessClientTransmitRate
colubrisWirelessClientTransmitRate.description: Current data transmission rate of the station. Rates are set in increments of 500 Kb/s from 1 Mb/s to 63.5 Mb/s.

colubrisWirelessClientReceiveRate.name: colubrisWirelessClientReceiveRate
colubrisWirelessClientReceiveRate.description: Current receive rate of the station. Rates are set in increments of 500 Kb/s from 1 Mb/s to 63.5 Mb/s.
